        <thead>
          <tr><th>Method</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>await ctx.fadeOut(ms?)</code></td><td>Fade the screen to black over the given duration (default ~300ms).</td></tr>
