      <h5>Direct Subsystem Access</h5>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Property</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>ctx.state</code></td><td>Direct access to the StateStore (flags, variables, object states, visited rooms).</td></tr>
